==English==

===Interjection===
'''psst''', or '''psssst''' or '''pssssssst''' with as many 's' as needed to get the meaning across
# ''An interjection that implies the speaker is sending secret or whispered information to another person''
#:'''''Psst''', John, don't tell anyone, but I've got lots of candy stashed away.''
